    summary:
      "Lady Blomfield recalls scenes from ‘Abdu’l-Bahá’s Paris sojourn, where children, the poor, artists, and seekers felt His transforming presence.",
    source: "https://bahaiworld.bahai.org/library/memories-of-the-sojourn-of-abdul-baha-in-paris/",
